---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Florida Medical Marijuana Card Renewal Guide" 
  description="Keep your recommendations active. Learn the exact steps to renew your Florida medical marijuana card and physician orders with Releaf MD."
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="bg-brand-mint py-16 lg:py-24 border-b border-brand-primary/10">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center space-y-4">
      <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1 bg-brand-accent/10 text-brand-accent rounded-full text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">
        🔄 Renewal Services
      </span>
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-serif-headline text-brand-dark leading-tight uppercase">Florida Medical Marijuana Card Renewal</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        Keep your state-mandated orders active and avoid lapses in dispensary access. Follow our simple two-part renewal guide.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Content Section -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="bg-white border border-brand-primary/10 rounded-3xl p-8 sm:p-12 shadow-whisper prose prose-slate max-w-none space-y-8">
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif-headline text-brand-dark">The Two Types of Florida Renewals</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Many patients get confused by the dual-tracking nature of Florida's medical cannabis system. To stay legal and active, you must track two separate expiration dates:
        </p>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-8">
          <div class="bg-brand-mint/40 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-brand-primary/10 flex flex-col justify-between">
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-serif-headline font-bold text-brand-dark text-base mb-2">1. Physician Certification (Every 30 Weeks)</h3>
              <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">
                Florida Department of Health rules limit active recommendations to 210 days (30 weeks). To buy from dispensaries, your doctor must enter new orders before the active period expires.
              </p>
            </div>
            <a href="/evaluations" class="inline-block mt-4 text-xs font-bold text-brand-primary hover:text-brand-accent hover:underline">
              Related: Learn about evaluations &rarr;
            </a>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-brand-mint/40 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-brand-primary/10 flex flex-col justify-between">
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-serif-headline font-bold text-brand-dark text-base mb-2">2. State ID Card Renewal (Annually)</h3>
              <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">
                Your physical registry card expires every 12 months. This is completed directly on the Florida Medical Marijuana Use Registry (OMMU) portal, requiring a passport-style photo and a state fee of $75.
              </p>
            </div>
            <span class="inline-block mt-4 text-xs font-bold text-slate-400">
              Completed via State Portal
            </span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif-headline text-brand-dark">How to Renew Your Medical Marijuana Card in Florida</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Renewing your medical marijuana card in Florida is simple with Releaf MD. If you are an established patient, we help you renew on schedule:
        </p>
        
        <ol class="list-decimal pl-5 space-y-4 text-slate-600 text-sm">
          <li>
            <strong>Check Your Expiration Date:</strong> Log into the Florida Medical Marijuana Use Registry to verify when your active orders or card expire. We recommend scheduling your renewal 3 to 4 weeks early.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Book Your Renewal Assessment:</strong> Schedule your follow-up appointment with Dr. Kelly Ennix King. Eligible established patients may complete their renewal consultations via secure telehealth.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Submit Registry Fees (if annual):</strong> If your annual card is expiring, submit your renewal application and $75 processing fee through the online OMMU portal.
          </li>
        </ol>

        <div class="bg-brand-dark text-white p-8 rounded-2xl border-l-4 border-brand-accent my-10 space-y-4">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-serif-headline text-brand-mint uppercase">Established Telehealth Options</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
            Florida law allows telemedicine consultations for established renewal evaluations. Save a trip to the office by scheduling a remote video consult with Dr. Kelly. Call or request a slot to see if you qualify.
          </p>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif-headline text-brand-dark">Consequences of Letting Your Recommendations Expire</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          If your 70-day or 210-day physician orders lapse, Florida dispensaries cannot sell you medical cannabis, even if your physical state card is still active. Keep your care uninterrupted by staying in touch with Releaf MD and booking your renewal visits on time.
        </p>

        <div class="border-t border-slate-100 pt-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-4">
          <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 italic">
            Read our <a href="/florida-medical-marijuana-card-guide" class="text-brand-primary font-bold hover:underline">Complete Florida Card Guide</a>.
          </p>
          <a href="https://live.vcita.com/site/DrKellyKing" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="bg-brand-accent hover:bg-brand-primary text-white font-bold px-6 py-3 rounded-full text-xs uppercase transition-colors shadow-md active-press">
            Book Renewal Now
          </a>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
